A retired high school teacher and family member of RA Moodley Spices business owners, Mrs Moodliar, was found murdered at her residence in Sparks Road, Overport, on Sunday morning, 03 May 2020.According to a family member who wished to remain anonymous, it is alleged that the former teacher was gagged and strangled. The source further alleged that Moodliar’s killers were known to her.As per the family member, the victim’s valuables were stolen before the suspects, believed to be two males, fled the scene. Police and forensic teams were at the scene and investigations into the cold-blooded killing are underway. 